replies.body:
@Meddler Hey, this is kind of an old thread, but can I ask you why Yorick didn't get any mana compensation buffs? He's in my experience one of the most mana-hungry champs there is, and I buy mana pots with him throughout the game - early, mid, and late game.

And I know a lot of Yorick players like to build straight into Sapphire Crystal and many times don't go with a "starting item" so even if the new starting items might help, it's unfortunate that he will be forced into it at that point.

I know he's not the most exciting champion, and a lot of people forget about him (which is why he didn't get a buff..?) so please help {{champion:83}} !!! There are far less mana-hungry champions that received buffs while this guy didn't. Can you fix that?
